<p><b>Overview:</b> A <em><b>Song</b></em> is made of 
	<em><b>Sections</b></em>, and <em><b>Sections</b></em> are made of 
	<em><b>Parts</b></em>.</p>


<div id="overview-visual" class="omg-song">
